result.longName: Moshi Moshi Retail Corporation Public Company Limited

assetProfile.address2: Bang Khun Thian Subdistrict Chom Thong District
assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Moshi Moshi Retail Corporation Public Company Limited engages in the retail and wholesale of lifestyle products in Thailand. It sells home furnishings, bags, pens, pencils, notebooks, stickers, rulers, folders, plush toys, fashion items, t-shirts, long sleeves, shorts, pajamas, beauty accessories, hats, scarves, sunglasses, shoes, perfumes, hand creams, and body lotions. The company also offers IT equipment, bluetooth speakers, headphones, mobile phone chargers, toys, food and drink products, cloth masks, keychains, eyebrow pencils, lipsticks, candies, COVID-19 testing kits, rugs, picture frames, and artificial plants. In addition, the company sells its products online. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Bangkok, Thailand.
